quran[112]{c,v,t}:
  21,1,"Okhuyasibwa khwa abandu khuli hambi, nabo bali mukhung’ang’ala nibalechele."
  21,2,"Ne shikabetselanga amachelo amacheni okhurula khu Nyasaye wabu Omulesi halali bakawulilanga nibakakholela omubayo."
  21,3,"Emioyo chiabu chakosania, mana balia abamabii bemonyelesinjia mbu: “Uno niwina halali ni Omundusa shinga enywe. Koo, mutsitsanga khubulosi nanyu nimulola?”"
  21,4,"Yaboola mbu: “Nyasaye wanje Omulesi yamanya amakhuwa akaboolungwa mwikulu nende khushialo, naye ni omuwulili muno, omumanyi muno.”"
  21,5,"Halali (abakhayi) baboola mbu: “(Akaaboolanga ako) ni amalooro katsokaana, halali akakasinjia omwene, ye ni omwimbi wa amashairi. Kho, akhurererekhwo eshimanyisio shingala aba imbeli barumwa.”"
  21,6,"Ne shibaasubira abali imbeli wabu okhurula buli mulukongo lwakhwasishia tawe, kho bano balasuubila?"
  21,7,"Ne shikhwaruma imbeli wuwo halali abasatsa bakhwafimbulilanga. Kho, rebe Abandu betsulilanga nikali mbu shimumanyile tawe."
  21,8,"Ne shikhwabakhola (Abarumwa abo) okhuba emibili chilalia ebilibwa tawe, ne shibali bookhumenya tsinyanga tsiosi tawe."
  21,9,"Mana nikhubakholela shinga khwabalaka, mana nikhubahabina nende abakhwenya okhuhabina, ne nikhusishia ababusia eshichero khubukholi bwa tsimbi."
  21,10,"Toto khwabeshilia eshitabu eshilimwo ametsulisio kenyu. Koo, shimwikhonyeranga obwongo tawe?"
  21,11,"Ne ni tsingongo tsinga etsiakhwanyasia etsiali nitsikholanga amabii, mana nikhuloonga inyuma wabu abandu bandi?"
  21,12,"Ne olwa balola eshinyasio shiefu, mana hawo nibachaka okhushilukha."
  21,13,"""Mulelukha tawe, kalukhe khubwokholo bwamwahelesibwa nende mubimenyo bienyu khomunyoole okhureebwa."""
  21,14,"Baboola mbu: “Abaane toto efwe khwali abamabii.”"
  21,15,"Ne nibatsililila okhulila khwabu okho okhula shingala khwabakhola shinga babererwe, basimile (bafwile)."
  21,16,"Ne shikhwalonga likulu nende eshialo nende ebili hakari wabio khumubayo tawe."
  21,17,"Nekhwenyanga okhukhola omubayo, khwakhekholele efwe abeene, (sikhwakhabarere hakari tawe) toto khubetsanga abakholanga omubayo."
  21,18,"Halali khusukunanga obwatoto khububeyi, mana bubufunake (obubeyi obo), mana buruleho olwene olo. Ne toto muli nende eshinyasio eshilulu shibalindanga khukamuboolanga ako."
  21,19,"Ne ni ebibie bioosi bili mwikulu nende khushialo, ne abali ewuwe shibakholanga obufuru okhumulaama nohomba shibachonyanga tawe."
  21,20,"Bamutswenulanga eshilo neshitere, ne shibachonyanga tawe."
  21,21,"Nohomba babukula abanyasaye khushialo abalamusinjia?"
  21,22,"Balabakhowo abanyasaye bandi (mwikulu nende khushialo) abalali Nyasaye tawe, toto hawo (likulu nende eshialo) biakhabiyile. Kho obutswenufu bwoosi ni bwa Nyasaye, Omwami weshisaala shia obuami (Arsh) ne ali ehale nende akabamuboolangakhwo ako."
  21,23,"Shareebungwa akakholanga tawe, halali bo balirebwa."
  21,24,"Nohomba bekholela Abanyasaye bandi abalali Nyasaye tawe? Boola mbu; “Rere ebifune bienyu. Kano ni ametsulisio ka bano abali halala ninasi, khandi nametsulisio khu balia abali inyuma wanje.” Halali abaanji mubo shibamanyile obwatieli tawe, kho mana shibakabukulilangamwo oluchendo tawe."
  21,25,"Ne shikhwarumakhwo Omurumwa yesiyesi imbeli wuwo tawe halali khwamufimbulila mbu: “Abulaho nyasaye wundi halali esie, kho, munaame esiesa.”"
  21,26,"Ne (abakhayi) baboola mbu: “Omunji wetsimbabaasi yeekholela Omwana.” Obutswenufu nobubwe. Shineendio tawe, abo ni Abasumba aboluyali."
  21,27,"Shibamuranjililangakhwo khulikhuwa tawe, nabo bakholanga amalomesio keke."
  21,28,"Amanyile akali imbeli wabu nende inyuma wabu, ne shibasabilanga tawe halali ulia wa Nyasaye achamile, nabo behotselesinjia khulwa okhumuria."
  21,29,"Ne ulia uboola mubo (abamalaika ) mbu: “Esie endi nyasaye owulali Nyasaye”, oyo khwitsa okhumurunga Jahannamu. Endio nilwa khurunganga abamabii."
  21,30,"Koo, abakhayi shibalolangakhwo mbu likulu nende eshialo biali biatilana mana nikhubikabukhasia, ne nikhukhola okhurula khumatsi buli eshindu okhuba eshilamu? Kho mana shibakhasuubilanga tawe?"
  21,31,"Ne nikhura khwiloba ebikulu kho (liloba) lilababeyiabeyia tawe, ne nikhuramwo tsinjila kho banyoole okhulunjikha."
  21,32,"Ne nikhukhola likulu okhuba eshitsafu eshialindwa, halali bo babulilanga oluchendo ebimanyisio bibie."
  21,33,"Naye niye owaloonga eshilo nende eshitere, nende eliuba nende omwesi, bioosi bibenganga khulunyaali lwabotokhana nibimwitsoomia."
  21,34,"Nafu shikhwakholelakhwo Omundu yesiyesi imbeli wuwo okhumenya tsinyanga tsioosi tawe, kho koo ewe nofwa, kho nabo nibo balimenya tsinyanga tsioosi?"
  21,35,"Buli Omundu alipila lifwa, ne khulabatema khumabii nende amalayi, ne ewefu niwa mwesi mulikalusibwa."
  21,36,"Ne abakhayi nibakhulola, shibakhukholelanga eshindu tawe halali omubayo mbu: “Koo, uno niye uboolanga (obubii) khubanyasaye benyu?” Ne bo nibo abakhayanga ametsulisio ka Omunji wetsimbabaasi."
  21,37,"Omundu yalongwa mubuyungubafu. Hambi hano nditsa okhubechesia ebimanyisio bianje khomulayungubasia tawe."
  21,38,"Ne baboolanga mbu: “Akabakhulakanga kano kaliba lina toto nimuli mbu muboolanga akatoto?”"
  21,39,"Abakhayi bamanyangakhwo ebise biabalikhaywa okhwikalila omulilo okhula khu bweni bwabu nende khumikongo chiabu, ne shibalikhoonywa tawe."
  21,40,"Ne (Isaa yeyindukho) iliboolela mapwoka mana ibang’ang’asie, ne shibalinyala okhuikalusia tawe, ne shibalihebwa obwiyangu tawe."
  21,41,"Ne toto Abarumwa abali imbeli wuwo bakholelwa omubayo, kho balia abakholanga omubayo mubo kalibanyoola kalia akabakholelanga omubayo."
  21,42,"Boola mbu: “Ni wina unyala okhubalinda eshilo nende eshitere ehale nende Omunji wetsimbabaasi?” Halali bo okhwitsulila Nyasaye wabu Omulesi khubabulilanga oluchendo."
  21,43,"Koo, bali nende abanyasaye babalindanga okhulana ninafwe? Shibanyala okhwikhonya abene tawe (Abanyasaye abo), ne shibalilindwa okhurulana ninafu tawe (nikhwenya okhubasandia)."
  21,44,"Halali khwelesia obwokholo bano nende bapapa babu okhuula obulamu bwabu nibubarambiyila. Shibalolangakhwo mbu efwe khutilanga liloba liabu nikhulitutuyia mutsimbeka tsialio? Kho koo, bo nibo balishila?"
  21,45,"Boola mbu: “Esie ebekanyilisinjia khubufimbuli (bwa Nyasaye). Ne Abatimbe shibawulilanga omulango nibekanyilisibwa tawe.”"
  21,46,"Ne batilungwa nende eshikhupo shilala butswa shia eshinyasio shia Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi, toto bakhaboolele mbu: “Eee baane efwe, toto khwali Abandu ababii.”"
  21,47,"Nafu khuliraho ebichelo biobuleng’afu inyanga yeyindukho, ne Omundu yesiyesi shalikholelwa obubii kata hatiti tawe. Kata likhuwa elo nililiba nende obusiro obutiti shinga olufwa lwa khardal (olufwa lwelitoto), khulilirera, nafu khuyela obulai okhuba abamanyi bokhubala."
  21,48,"Ne toto khwahelesia Musa nende Haruni Eshiawukhasinjia, nende obulafu, nende ametsulisilio khubalia baria Nyasaye."
  21,49,"Balia baritsanga Nyasaye wabu Omulesi khubwifise, ne bo khandi baritsanga muno inyanga yeyindukho."
  21,50,"Ne buno ni obwitsulisio bwetsimbabaasi obwakhwabeshilia. Kho enywe mubwikananga?"
  21,51,"Ne toto khwahelesia Ibrahim obulunjifu bubwe khale awo, ne khwali khwamumanya muno."
  21,52,"Olwa yaboolela samwana nende Abandu bebe mbu: “Ne bino ni ebifwanani shina ebya mwikhalilangaho ebise biosi (okhubilama)?”"
  21,53,"Nibaboola mbu: “Khwanyoola bapapa befu nibabilamanga, (kho mana fwesi khubilamanga).”"
  21,54,"Naboola mbu: “Toto enywe nende basenywe mwali mubukori obuli habulafu.”"
  21,55,"Nibaboola mbu: “Koo, okhwitsile khubwatoto nohomba oli mubalia bakholangasa omubayo?”"
  21,56,"Naboola mbu: “(Shikali kario tawe) halali Nyasaye wenyu Omulesi ni Nyasaye Omulesi wa likulu nende eshialo, ulia owabiloonga. Nasi endi mulala khubaloli baako."
  21,57,"Ne nditsuba khu Nyasaye mbu toto nditsa okhukholela eshifwanga ebifwanani bienyu bino nimwakhamala okhubifutarira mwakhatsia."""
  21,58,"Mana nabitonyatonya ebitonye halali eshifwanani eshikhongo shiabu kho banyoole okhushikalukhakhwo."
  21,59,"Baboola mbu: “Ni wina ukholeele kano abanyasaye befu? Toto ye ali mubandu bamabii muno.”"
  21,60,"Nibaboola mbu: “Khuwulile Omusiani mulala nabarumbulanga. Alangwa mbu Ibrahim.”"
  21,61,"Nibaboola mbu: “Nakhamurere imbeli mutsimoni tsia Abandu, banyoole okhwilolela.”"
  21,62,"Nibaboola mbu: “Koo, newe ukholeele ori Abanyasaye befu ewe Ibrahim?”"
  21,63,"Naboola mbu: “Tawe, halali ukholele ni omukhongo wabu oyo, kho mubareebe toto nikali mbu banyala okhulomaloma.”"
  21,64,"Nibeekalukhakhwo abene, nibaboola mbu; “Toto enywe muli Abandu bamabii.”"
  21,65,"Mana nibakalukha mubukori bwabu bulia (nibaboola mbu): “Toto wamanya obulai mbu bino shibilomalomanga tawe.”"
  21,66,"Naboola mbu: “Koo, mulaamanga habundu wa Nyasaye ebilabakhoonya shiosishiosi nohomba okhubakhola obubii tawe?"
  21,67,"Ooh eshifimbwa murwe khwinywe nende ebiamulaamanga habundu wa Nyasaye. Koo shimuparangakhwo tawe?”"
  21,68,"Nibaboola mbu: “Mumusambe mumulilo ne muhabine abanyasaye benyu toto nimuli abokhukhola likhuwa.”"
  21,69,"Khwaboola mbu: “Ewe omulilo, ba omunyifu nomulembe khu Ibrahimu.”"
  21,70,"Ne bamwenyela amabii, mana nikhubakhola nibaba nibo bokhunyoola obusishi muno."
  21,71,"Ne nikhumuhabina ye nende Luti, nikhubayila khuliloba liakhwaramwo tsimbabaasi shichila ebiloonje bioosi (Sham)."
  21,72,"Mana nikhumuhelesia Is-haka (okhuba omwana wuwe) nende Yaqub okhuba omwitsukhulu, ne boosi nikhubakhola okhuba abalayi."
  21,73,"Nenikhubakhola okhuba abemilisi abemililanga khulikhuwa liefu, ne nikhubafimbulila okhukhola amalayi, nende okhulumilila okhulaama nende okhurusia eshihanwa shia Izakaa. Ne bali abehotselefu khwifwe."
  21,74,"Ne Luti nikhumuhelesia oburuchi nende obumanyi, ne nikhumuhabina okhurulana nende olukongo olwakholanga amabii, toto bo bali Abandu ababii, abafunachi bamalako."
  21,75,"Ne nikhumwinjisia mutsimbabaasi tsiefu. Toto ye yali mubakholi bamalayi."
  21,76,"Ne Nuhu olwoyalanga imbeli awo, nafu nikhumufuchilila, nikhumuhabina ye nende Abandu bebe okhurula khubutinyu obukhongo."
  21,77,"Mana nikhumuhabina okhurulana nende abandu bayingasia ebimanyisio biefu. Toto abo bali Abandu ababii mana nikhubasishia boosi."
  21,78,"Nende Daudi nende Suleiman, olwa benya okhukhalaka eshina okhulondokhana nende omukunda, olwa tsimbusi tsiabandu tsialiamwo eshilo, nafu mubukhalachi bwabu obo khwali abaloli."
  21,79,"Mana nikhumanyia Suleiman (okhushila omukofu wuwe Daudi). Ne buli mulala wabu nikhumuhelesia obukhalachi bweshina nende obumanyi. Ne nikhukhola Daudi nende tsingulu okhuba nende oburechelefu khwifwe, halala nende amayoni okhumutswenula (Nyasaye), ne endio nilwa khwakhola."
  21,80,"Ne nikhumwechesia (Daudi) okhukasia tsingubo tsienyu tsieliyie, kho tsibalinde okhurulana nende obulwani bwenyu. Koo enywe shimuli bakhupa orio tawe?"
  21,81,"Ne Suleiman nikhumukholela omuyeka kweyimbumbuyeka okhumuwulila kuwutsanga khukhulomesia khukhwe khushialo eshiakhwaramwo tsimbabaasi, nafu nefwe abamanyi babuli eshindu."
  21,82,"Ne nikhumukholela amashetani akeyibilanga munyanza okhumurerera ebisole (lulu), ne bamukholelanga emilimo chindi chilali echo tawe, ne efwe khwali abalindi babu."
  21,83,"Ne Ayubu olwa yalanga Nyasaye wuwe Omulesi mbu: “Toto esie obunyakhani bwandiila, ne ewe newe Omunji wetsimbabaasi.”"
  21,84,"Mana nikhumuwulila ne nikhumuhiniliaho obunyakhani bubwe obo, ne nikhumuhelesia abandu bebe nende shingabo halala tsimbabaasi okhurula khwifwe, nende obwitsulisio khubilonje bioosi."
  21,85,"Ne Ismail, nende Idris, nende Dhilkifl, boosi bali mubesumilisi."
  21,86,"Ne nikhubenjisia mutsimbabaasi tsiefu. Toto abo bali mubandu abalayi."
  21,87,"Ne Dhanun (Yunus) olwa yarula nasinyishe naparanga mbu shikhulamunyala tawe, mana nalaanga mushiilima mbu: “Abulaho Nyasaye wundi tawe owulali ewe. Toto esie embeele mubandu ababii.”"
  21,88,"Mana nikhumufuchilila, ne nikhumuhabina okhurulana nende eshibeela esho. Ne endio nilwa khuhabinanga Abasuubili."
  21,89,"Ne Zakaria olwa yalaanga Nyasaye wuwe Omulesi mbu: “Nyasaye wanje Omulesi, olandekha sienyene tawe, ne newe omulayi muno wokhuhelesia.”"
  21,90,"Mana nikhumufuchilila ne nikhumuhelesia Yahya, ne nikhumukasilia omukhaye wuwe. Toto abo bali abangu muno bokhukhola amalayi, ne bakhusabanga khubwikombi nende oburi, ne bali abehotselefu khwifwe."
  21,91,"Ne Omukhasi welinda omubili kukwe, mana nikhumufuriramwo okhurulana nende omwoyo kwefu, mana nikhumukhola ye nende Omwana wuwe okhuba eshilolelo khubilonje bioosi."
  21,92,"Toto omukanda kwenyu kuno ni omukanda mulala, nasi nesie Nyasaye wenyu (mulala) Omulesi, kho munaame."
  21,93,"Nabo nibaukhana hakari wabu likhuwa liabu lino (nibakabukhana), boosi balikalukha khwifwe."
  21,94,"Ne ulakhola ebikhole ebilayi naye nali omusuubili, obukhalabani bubwe shibulikhaywa tawe. Ne toto efwe khumuhandichilanga."
  21,95,"Ne kamala okhukanibwa mbu, olukongo lwakhwasishia mbu bo shibalikalukha tawe."
  21,96,"Okhuula shingala Yajuji nende Maajuji balilekhulwa, nebalikholomokha okhurula buli khutsingulu (awo indukho ilibayulile)."
  21,97,"Ne indache yatoto olwayiliula, awo niwo wetsimoni tsiabakhayi tsilikandaala, baliboola mbu: “Abaane … khwali mubukoyani khukano, ne toto khwali Abandu ababii.”"
  21,98,"Toto enywe nende ebiamulaamanga ebilali Nyasaye tawe, muli tsikhwi tsiomulilo kwa Jahannam, toto enywe mulikwinjilamwo."
  21,99,"Abo babetsanga abanyasaye shibakhenjilemwo (Jahannam) tawe, nabo balikhalamwo tsinyanga tsiosi."
  21,100,"Eliabu omo abo balibasa bokhupa obuyoka, ne shibaliwulila (elibahotselesia) tawe."
  21,101,"Toto balia bobulayi bwefu buliulila, abo baliba ehale ninakwo (omulilo kwa Jahannam)."
  21,102,"Shibaliwulila okhupupuchila khwakwo tawe, nabo balinyoola akemioyo chiabu chikoomba tsinyanga tsiosi."
  21,103,"Shibalibeelesibwa nende omuresio omukhongo kulia tawe, ne Abamalaika balibabukanila nibababoolela mbu: “Ino niyo inyanga yenyu eyamwalakungwa.”"
  21,104,"Inyanga yakhulifuumba likulu shingala khufumbanga tsimbapulo tsiahandikwakhwo. Shingala khwabaloonga olwokhuranga, khulibakalusia khandi endio. Ni indache ili khwifwe. Toto efwe ni bokhukholako."
  21,105,"Ne toto khwahandika mu Zaburi nikhumalile okhuhandika khulubao olwalindwa (Lawhul mahfudh) mbu: “Eshialo shino (shilichelamwa) nende Abasumba banje abalayi.”"
  21,106,"Toto mukano kalimwo amachelo khubandu balaamanga Nyasaye."
  21,107,"Ne shikhwakhuruma halali obe tsimbabaasi khubandu boosi."
  21,108,"Boola mbu: “Esie toto efimbulilungwa mbu Nyasaye wenyu ni Nyasaye mulala butswa, kho enywe mumalile okhuba abeesilamu?”"
  21,109,"Ne nibaloba, boola mbu: “Eboosiliye obulayi, ne engorerwe mbu kali ahambi nohomba kali ehale kalia akamulakungwa.”"
  21,110,"Toto ye amanyile likhuwa elia habulafu, ne amanyile akamufisanga."
  21,111,"Ne engorerwe, khaundi kano naamatemo khwinywe nohomba obwokholo khubise ebititi."
  21,112,"Naboola mbu: “Nyasaye wanje Omulesi, khalaka eshina khubwatoto. Ne Nyasaye wefu Omulesi niye Omunji wetsimbabaasi, Owusabungwa obukhoonyi khu ako kamuboolanga akobubeyi."""
